Properties.commandText: IF SCHEMA_ID(N'usr') IS NULL EXEC(N'CREATE SCHEMA [usr];');

CREATE TABLE [usr].[Roles] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [DisplayName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [CreatedDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [NormalizedName] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [ConcurrencyStamp] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Roles] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[Users] (
    [UserId] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [FamilyName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [GeneratedCode] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [UserName] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [NormalizedUserName] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [NormalizedEmail] nvarchar(256) NULL,
    [EmailConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [PasswordHash] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [SecurityStamp] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [ConcurrencyStamp] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [PhoneNumber] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [PhoneNumberConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [TwoFactorEnabled] bit NOT NULL,
    [LockoutEnd] datetimeoffset NULL,
    [LockoutEnabled] bit NOT NULL,
    [AccessFailedCount] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Users] PRIMARY KEY ([UserId])
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[RoleClaims] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [CreatedClaim] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [RoleId] int NOT NULL,
    [ClaimType] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [ClaimValue] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_RoleClaims] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RoleClaims_Roles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Roles] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[UserClaims] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [ClaimType] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [ClaimValue] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserClaims] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserClaims_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[UserLogins] (
    [LoginProvider] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [ProviderKey] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [LoggedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [ProviderDisplayName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserLogins] PRIMARY KEY ([LoginProvider], [ProviderKey]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserLogins_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[UserRefreshTokens] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsValid] bit NOT NULL,
    [CreatedTime] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [ModifiedDate] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserRefreshTokens] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRefreshTokens_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[UserRoles] (
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [RoleId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedUserRoleDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserRoles] PRIMARY KEY ([UserId], [RoleId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Roles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Roles] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [usr].[UserTokens] (
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [LoginProvider] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [GeneratedTime] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [Value] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserTokens] PRIMARY KEY ([UserId], [LoginProvider], [Name]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserTokens_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX [RoleNameIndex] ON [usr].[Roles] ([NormalizedName]) WHERE [NormalizedName] IS NOT NULL;
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX [UserNameIndex] ON [usr].[Users] ([NormalizedUserName]) WHERE [NormalizedUserName] IS NOT NULL;

CREATE TABLE [Orders] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [OrderName] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedTime] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [ModifiedDate] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Orders] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [usr].[Users] ([UserId]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);
ALTER TABLE [Orders] ADD [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL DEFAULT CAST(0 AS bit);
